{"tid":1772948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致200萬和理非","createTime":"2019-12-07T05:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T06:37:49.000Z","uid":332189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b59b88280b6ddcb53c571eaac8c505b32b536a4","tid":1772948,"uid":332189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"少少心底話<br />\n <br />\n「點解616肯行出嚟？」<br />\n因為6月9日有一百萬人遊行，垃圾政府只係應我地一句「哦」，然後照舊二讀！<br />\n因為612係警暴嘅開始，再一次亂放催淚彈。<br />\n因為暴政逼死我地嘅義士，如果我地連遊行獻花都懶得做，實在有愧於心。<br />\n而家呢？大大小小嘅記者會，逼香港人聽埋咁多廢話，都係無真真正正回應民意。<br />\n警暴一次比一次誇張，1萬粒催淚彈我地唔可以習以為常。<br />\n幾千位手足被拘捕，不計其數嘅義士離開人世，我地又講得過去？<br />\n <br />\n「點解之後咁多遊行又唔再出嚟？」<br />\n因為無不反對知書，犯法喎。<br />\n而家有啦！今次大型遊行有啦！<br />\n <br />\n「黎明行動嗰個星期你做緊咩野？」<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;返工&hellip;&hellip;但我完全唔介意交通受阻，理解佢地發起不合作運動。有時我喺企滿人巴士或者經過人來人往嘅街，喺到諗，如果每7個就有2個企過出嚟，點解而家可以咁無情咁如常返工？（咁諗得，我就係其中一個）返工先搵到錢，搵到錢先有錢捐嘛。唔係，其實一句到尾係「自私」。<br />\n <br />\n「救Poly嗰晚你又做緊咩？」<br />\n......放工返屋企&hellip;&hellip;但我有一直留意住新聞，睇直播，睇到嬲！但對件事亳無幫助&hellip;我成日都覺得自己好廢，覺得好無力。係自私，係驚。有時無稍為勇喞朋友一齊去，一個出去又驚。<br />\n <br />\n而家呢？星期日放假啦！唔洗返工啦！<br />\n12.8出嚟已經唔單單係講初心，呢六個月發生嘅事，我地一世都唔會忘記！<br />\n&ldquo;等我為大家回憶下再決定1208去唔去&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772471</a><br />\n<br />\n如果聽日都唔出嚟，唔該唔好再同人講自己係一個「和理非」。<br />\n遊行係我地嘅嘅自由，係我地嘅選擇，唔係由警方放唔放催淚彈主導。<br />\n我唔會知道哂呢200萬人係邊個，但你一定知道自己身邊有邊個喺616出過去。懇請你地再一次嗌埋佢地，塞爆港島！<br />\n仲有，希望聽日見到第2,000,002個嘅你！"},{"pid":"2c1781ee3311e7d483ffba02ac6928a0608dcca2","tid":1772948,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"又話支持又唔想出嚟個班<br />\n好好諗下出咗去嘅手足<br />\n越多人越安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb55086d335241647ffa14129fc07071b30da7","tid":1772948,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa992e0d97f3e8f09fc0dd268efdeabeec6bebd0","tid":1772948,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f828a40b95252b838aadc90bb338b71ae7dde24d","tid":1772948,"uid":332189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1781ee3311e7d483ffba02ac6928a0608dcca2","tid":1772948,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"又話支持又唔想出嚟個班<br />\n好好諗下出咗去嘅手足<br />\n越多人越安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"諗返616，就係夠多人先逼到佢開路，夠多人佢先唔敢亂驅散！"},{"pid":"13676f41861466f8b13a71d69a3bf7a2bbabeead","tid":1772948,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}